Scripts for running Millepede-II and reconversion.
You can set this directory anywhere

Assume that
- run CKF2GlobalAlignment with cluster and side by side
- convert2mille_v2_ss.C was processed.

(1.conversion)

2.First pede
3st
mp2str-noIFT-2layersfixed_v2_ss.txt
4st
mp2str-withIFT-2layersfixed_v2_ss.txt

3.Prepare for Second pede
makeFixAnotherLayers.sh

4.Second pede
3st
mp2str-noIFT-anotherlayersfixed_v2_ss.txt
4st
mp2str-withIFT-anotherlayersfixed_v2_ss.txt

5.Reconcersion
reconversion_ss.sh
